'''迪塞普遜島'''<ref name="新华网迪塞普逊岛">{{cite web|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com//world/2016-01/26/c_128670723.htm|title=走进南极 感受冰雪世界之美|date=2016-01-26|accessdate=2018-12-18|work=[[新华网|新华网]]|archive-date=2018-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181218145632/http://www.xinhuanet.com//world/2016-01/26/c_128670723.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>（{{lang-en|Deception Island}}）是[[南極洲|南極洲]]的[[火山島|火山島]]，位於[[南極大陸|南極大陸]]對開海域，屬於[[南設得蘭群島|南設得蘭群島]]的一部分，長14.4公里、寬12.2公里，面積136.9平方公里，最高點[[海拔|海拔]]高度576米<ref name="gvp">{{cite gvp|vnum=390030|name=Deception Island|accessdate=2018-12-18}}</ref>，最近一次[[火山噴發|火山噴發]]在1970年發生<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/271196032_The_1970_eruption_on_Deception_Island_Antarctica_Eruptive_dynamics_and_implications_for_volcanic_hazards |title=The 1970 eruption on Deception Island (Antarctica): eruptive dynamics and implications for volcanic hazards |accessdate=2018-12-04 |archive-date=2018-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181204102021/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/271196032_The_1970_eruption_on_Deception_Island_Antarctica_Eruptive_dynamics_and_implications_for_volcanic_hazards |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於此島之東南部有一[[海峽|海峽]]，使其[[形狀|形狀]]似[[指環|指環]]，容易造成[[視錯覺|視錯覺]]（{{lang|en|Deception}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://data.aad.gov.au/aadc/gaz/scar/display_name.cfm?gaz_id=108460|title=SCAR Composite Gazetteer|website=www.data.aad.gov.au|access-date=2017-08-28|archive-date=2017-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170828105415/https://data.aad.gov.au/aadc/gaz/scar/display_name.cfm?gaz_id=108460|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因而得名。

此島上並無人居住，該島的領土主權問題，按[[南极条约体系|南极条约体系]]處理。島內的天然<ref>[http://www.twword.com/wiki/%E6%AC%BA%E9%A8%99%E5%B3%B6 欺騙島]. 台灣Word. 2013-07-15. </ref>[[港灣|港灣]]（natural sheltered harbour<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.deceptionisland.aq/ |title=Deception Island Management Group |accessdate=2013-04-13 |archive-date=2011-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110209211205/http://www.deceptionisland.aq/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>）是良好的避风港<ref>[https://www.abandonedspaces.com/uncategorized/deception-island.html  Deception Island: The “safest” harbor in Antarctica until it was abandoned in the 1960s] {{Wayback|url=https://www.abandonedspaces.com/uncategorized/deception-island.html |date=20181222173527 }} Abandoned Spaces. 2017-03-30.</ref>。

